item.title: What's wrong with my JDK
item.dc:creator: @CodeForFame CodeForFame
item.description:
@CodeForFame wrote:

[quote=“veer, post:13, topic:449232”]“Help, when I try to run my server I get an error, oh my god, this has never happened to me, I don’t know what to do!”

Does your server run with the latest stable release? Have you bothered to file an issue at their JIRA page? Have you tried looking for already submit issues that match your problem?[/quote]We’re using an extremely old version of XStream (I’m pretty sure it’s pre-1.2, but it may be 1.2), and there has been at least one code-breaking release between the one we use and the current one.

Anyway, it will take about the same amount of work to switch to a better format.
